    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Java的toString-方法"><a href="#Java的toString-方法" class="headerlink" title="Java的toString()方法"></a>Java的toString()方法</h1><p>在 Java 中，**<code>toString()</code> 方法** 是 <code>Object</code> 类提供的一个方法。由于所有类都继承自 <code>Object</code>，所以每个 Java 类都默认拥有 <code>toString()</code> 方法。如果你没有重写它，调用 <code>toString()</code> 方法时会使用默认实现。</p><hr><h3 id="默认的-toString-方法是什么？"><a href="#默认的-toString-方法是什么？" class="headerlink" title="默认的 toString() 方法是什么？"></a><strong>默认的 <code>toString()</code> 方法是什么？</strong></h3><p><code>Object</code> 类中的默认实现是这样的：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> String <span class="hljs-title function_">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> getClass().getName() + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;@&quot;</span> + Integer.toHexString(hashCode());<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也就是说，默认的 <code>toString()</code> 会返回：</p><ol><li>对象的 <strong>类名</strong>。</li><li>后跟 <code>@</code> 符号。</li><li>后跟对象的 <strong>哈希码</strong>（十六进制形式）。</li></ol><h4 id="示例："><a href="#示例：" class="headerlink" title="示例："></a>示例：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span> &#123;&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Main</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">Person</span> <span class="hljs-variable">person</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span>();<br>        System.out.println(person.toString());<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输出：</strong></p><figure class="highlight llvm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs llvm">Person<span class="hljs-title">@6</span>d<span class="hljs-number">06</span>d<span class="hljs-number">69</span><span class="hljs-keyword">c</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个字符串看起来没有太多实际意义，因此我们通常会 <strong>重写 <code>toString()</code> 方法</strong>，让它返回更易读的信息。</p><hr><h3 id="为什么初始化时要重写-toString-？"><a href="#为什么初始化时要重写-toString-？" class="headerlink" title="为什么初始化时要重写 toString()？"></a><strong>为什么初始化时要重写 <code>toString()</code>？</strong></h3><p>重写 <code>toString()</code> 方法的主要目的是 <strong>让对象更易于阅读和调试</strong>，尤其是在以下场景中：</p><ol><li><p><strong>调试和日志记录</strong>： 当我们打印一个对象时，<code>System.out.println(object);</code> 会自动调用该对象的 <code>toString()</code> 方法。如果 <code>toString()</code> 返回的是更具意义的信息（如对象的属性值），可以帮助开发者更直观地了解对象的状态。</p><h4 id="示例：-1"><a href="#示例：-1" class="headerlink" title="示例："></a>示例：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> String name;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> age;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Person</span><span class="hljs-params">(String name, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> age)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.name = name;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.age = age;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> String <span class="hljs-title function_">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Person&#123;name=&#x27;&quot;</span> + name + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#x27;, age=&quot;</span> + age + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#125;&quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Main</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">Person</span> <span class="hljs-variable">person</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Alice&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">25</span>);<br>        System.out.println(person); <span class="hljs-comment">// 自动调用 toString()</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输出：</strong></p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">Person&#123;<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Alice&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">age</span>=25&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这比默认的 <code>Person@6d06d69c</code> 更有意义。</p></li></ol><hr><ol><li><p><strong>提升代码可读性</strong>： 重写后的 <code>toString()</code> 方法可以提供类的关键信息，让代码更易理解。例如，当我们在集合中打印对象时，重写的 <code>toString()</code> 方法会显示对象的具体内容，而不是一串难以理解的哈希码。</p><h4 id="示例：-2"><a href="#示例：-2" class="headerlink" title="示例："></a>示例：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">List&lt;Person&gt; people = Arrays.asList(<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Alice&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">25</span>),<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Person</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Bob&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">30</span>)<br>);<br>System.out.println(people);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>输出：</strong></p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">[Person&#123;<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Alice&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">age</span>=25&#125;, Person&#123;<span class="hljs-attribute">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Bob&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">age</span>=30&#125;]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><ol><li><strong>与其他工具和框架的集成</strong>： 一些 Java 框架（如 Spring、Hibernate）会依赖 <code>toString()</code> 方法来打印对象信息。如果不重写 <code>toString()</code>，这些框架可能会打印出无意义的内容。</li></ol><hr><h3 id="如何重写-toString-？"><a href="#如何重写-toString-？" class="headerlink" title="如何重写 toString()？"></a><strong>如何重写 <code>toString()</code>？</strong></h3><p>通常，<code>toString()</code> 的重写逻辑是将对象的主要属性以一种易读的方式返回。建议的格式是：</p><ul><li>使用类名。</li><li>包含关键字段的值。</li></ul><h4 id="示例：-3"><a href="#示例：-3" class="headerlink" title="示例："></a>示例：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Car</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> String brand;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> String model;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> year;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Car</span><span class="hljs-params">(String brand, String model, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> year)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.brand = brand;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.model = model;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.year = year;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> String <span class="hljs-title function_">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Car&#123;brand=&#x27;&quot;</span> + brand + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#x27;, model=&#x27;&quot;</span> + model + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#x27;, year=&quot;</span> + year + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#125;&quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调用 <code>System.out.println(new Car(&quot;Toyota&quot;, &quot;Camry&quot;, 2023));</code> 时，输出会是：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">Car&#123;<span class="hljs-attribute">brand</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Toyota&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Camry&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">year</span>=2023&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="IDE-快捷生成-toString-方法"><a href="#IDE-快捷生成-toString-方法" class="headerlink" title="IDE 快捷生成 toString() 方法"></a><strong>IDE 快捷生成 <code>toString()</code> 方法</strong></h3><p>在 IntelliJ IDEA 或其他现代 IDE 中，你可以快速生成 <code>toString()</code> 方法。</p><h4 id="操作步骤："><a href="#操作步骤：" class="headerlink" title="操作步骤："></a>操作步骤：</h4><ol><li>在类中点击鼠标右键。</li><li>选择 <code>Generate</code> → <code>toString()</code>.</li><li>选择你希望包含在 <code>toString()</code> 中的字段。</li><li>IDE 会自动生成重写的 <code>toString()</code> 方法。</li></ol><hr><h3 id="总结：为什么重写-toString-？"><a href="#总结：为什么重写-toString-？" class="headerlink" title="总结：为什么重写 toString()？"></a><strong>总结：为什么重写 <code>toString()</code>？</strong></h3><ol><li><strong>提高调试效率</strong>：快速查看对象的关键属性。</li><li><strong>提升代码可读性</strong>：让打印对象时的输出更直观。</li><li><strong>便于框架集成</strong>：许多框架会调用 <code>toString()</code> 输出对象信息。</li><li><strong>简化日志记录</strong>：减少手动拼接属性值的代码。</li></ol><p>重写 <code>toString()</code> 是一种良好的编程习惯，尤其是在需要经常打印或检查对象状态的场景中。</p><h1 id="Java-的内部类"><a href="#Java-的内部类" class="headerlink" title="Java 的内部类"></a>Java 的内部类</h1><h2 id="1-什么是内部类"><a href="#1-什么是内部类" class="headerlink" title="1.什么是内部类"></a>1.什么是内部类</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">类的五大成员<br>    属性、方法、构造方法、代码块、内部类<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>定义：在一个类的里面，再定义一个类。</p><p>举例：在A类的内部定义B类，B类就被称为内部类</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Outer</span>&#123;(外部类)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Inner</span>&#123;(内部类)<br>        <br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Test</span>&#123;(外部其他类)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;<br>        <br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../images/%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB_1.png"></p><p><strong>什么时候用到内部类</strong>？</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css"><span class="hljs-selector-tag">B</span>类表示的事务是<span class="hljs-selector-tag">A</span>类的一部分，且<span class="hljs-selector-tag">B</span>单独存在没有意义。<br>比如：汽车的发动机、ArrayList的迭代器、人的心脏。。。<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-内部类的分类"><a href="#2-内部类的分类" class="headerlink" title="2.内部类的分类"></a>2.内部类的分类</h2><ul><li><strong>成员内部类</strong></li></ul><p><img src="/../images/%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB_1.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E5%9B%BE.png"></p><ul><li>静态内部类(也是成员内部类的一种)</li></ul><p><strong>静态内部类只能访问外部类中的静态变量和静态方法</strong></p><p><em>如果想访问非静态的需要创建外部类的对象。</em></p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB_%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB2.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB_%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB.png"></p><p>总结：</p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB_%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB3.png"></p><ul><li>局部内部类(没什么用~~~可以略过)</li></ul><p>将内部类定义在方法里面就叫做局部内部类，<strong>类似于方法里面的局部变量</strong>。</p><ul><li><strong>匿名内部类</strong></li></ul><p><strong>匿名内部类的本质</strong>：隐藏了名字的内部类。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">格式：<br><span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> 类名或者接口名()&#123;<br>    重写方法;<br>    &#125;<br><br>举例：<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Inter</span>()&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">show</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>看看这个你就能理解匿名内部类的实现方法了</strong></p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%B1%BB2.png"></p><h1 id="Java的泛型"><a href="#Java的泛型" class="headerlink" title="Java的泛型"></a>Java的泛型</h1><h2 id="1-泛型的背景和概述"><a href="#1-泛型的背景和概述" class="headerlink" title="1.泛型的背景和概述"></a>1.泛型的背景和概述</h2><p><img src="/../images/%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B_1.png"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Main</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//        System.out.println(&quot;Hello world!&quot;);</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        ArrayList list=new ArrayList();</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        list.add(&quot;java&quot;);</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        list.add(100);</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        list.add(true);</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        for (int i = 0; i &lt; list.size(); i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//            Object o=list.get(i);</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//            String str=(String)o;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//            System.out.println(str);</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//        &#125;</span><br><br><br>        ArrayList&lt;String&gt; strList=<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();<br>        strList.add(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;100&quot;</span>);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; strList.size(); i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">s</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> strList.get(i);<br>            System.out.println(s);<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>泛型的好处</strong></p><ul><li>编译期间检查类型</li><li>减少了数据类型转换</li></ul><p><img src="/../images/%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B_2.png"></p><h2 id="2-泛型类、接口"><a href="#2-泛型类、接口" class="headerlink" title="2.泛型类、接口"></a>2.泛型类、接口</h2><ul><li><strong>泛型类</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">class 类名称 &lt;泛型标识，泛型标识，...&gt;&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> 泛型标识 变量名;<br>    ......<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>常用的泛型标识</strong>:T、E、K、V</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">//泛型类的定义</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//&lt;T&gt; 泛型标识--类型形参</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//  T创建对象时指定具体的数据类型</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Generic</span>&lt;T&gt;&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> T key;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Generic</span><span class="hljs-params">(T key)</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.key=key;<br>    &#125;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> T <span class="hljs-title function_">getKey</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> key;<br>    &#125;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> T <span class="hljs-title function_">setKey</span><span class="hljs-params">(T key)</span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.key=key;<br>    &#125;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> String <span class="hljs-title function_">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Key&#123;key=&#x27;&quot;</span>+key+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#x27;&quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../images/%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B_3.png"></p><p><img src="/../images/%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B_4.png"></p><h2 id="3-从泛型类派生子类"><a href="#3-从泛型类派生子类" class="headerlink" title="3.从泛型类派生子类"></a>3.从泛型类派生子类</h2><p><img src="/../images/%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B%E7%B1%BB_6.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
